# devops-flow

Orchestrate Cloudflare deployments, GitHub PRs, and Slack notifications.

## MCP Configuration

MCP servers for this plugin are in `.cursor/mcp.json`. Environment variables use `${env:VAR_NAME}` syntax in Cursor.

> **Note:** This plugin uses Claude Code hooks which are not available in Cursor.
